Many manufacturers are focusing on sustainable and eco-friendly materials in the production of wireless headphones and keyboards to address environmental concerns.

17. What are the purchasing criteria for wireless headphones and keyboards?
Consumers consider factors such as sound quality, comfort, battery life, and price when purchasing wireless headphones and keyboards.

